{"word":"G5278 - ὑπομένω - hypoménō - hoop-om-en'-o - Abide","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπομένω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>hypoménō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hoop-om-en'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Abide"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நிலைத்திரு, தங்கியிரு, பொறுமையாயிரு, சகித்துக்கொள், பொறுமையோடு சகி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to remain, tarry behind"},{"paragraph":"2. to remain, abide"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G5259 - ὑπό - hypó - hoop-o'/5259\">G5259</a> and <a href=\"#/G3306 - μένω - ménō - men'-o/3306\">G3306</a>; to <i>stay under</i> (<i>behind</i>), that is, <i>remain</i>; figuratively to <i>undergo</i>, that is, <i>bear</i> (trials), <i>have fortitude</i>, <i>persevere:</i> - abide, endure, (take) patient (-ly), suffer, tarry behind."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1696 - ἐμμένω - emménō - em-men'-o/1696\">G1696</a>, <a href=\"#/G3306 - μένω - ménō - men'-o/3306\">G3306</a>, <a href=\"#/G3438 - μονή - monḗ - mon-ay'/3438\">G3438</a>, <a href=\"#/G3887 - παραμένω - paraménō - par-am-en'-o/3887\">G3887</a>, <a href=\"#/G4037 - περιμένω - periménō - per-ee-men'-o/4037\">G4037</a>, <a href=\"#/G5278 - ὑπομένω - hypoménō - hoop-om-en'-o/5278\">G5278</a>, <a href=\"#/G5281 - ὑπομονή - hypomonḗ - hoop-om-on-ay'/5281\">G5281</a>"}]}